description: Crazydilla Food Truck is roaming Miami and taking your typical quesadilla and turning it into a next level taste sensation! Home of "The Cubadilla," a spin on a traditional cuban sandwich with pulled pork, serrano ham and the works, Crazydilla takes several of your favorite sandwiches  and pulls their signature Crazy on them. But don't worry, Miami: The Crazydilla Truck offers a traditional Mexican quesadilla for the purists, as well.
name: Crazydilla Food Truck
